  • Classes in nl.naturalis.common.io used by nl.naturalis.common.io 
    Class Description
    ArraySwapOutputStream
    A SwapOutputStream that uses a byte array as internal buffer.
    DeflatedArraySwapOutputStream
    A SwapOutputStream that compresses the data as it enters the internal buffer, thereby decreasing the chance that the internal buffer will have to be swapped out to file.
    DeflatedNioSwapOutputStream
    A SwapOutputStream that compresses the data as it enters the internal buffer, thereby decreasing the chance that the internal buffer will have to be swapped out to file.
    NioSwapOutputStream
    A SwapOutputStream that uses java.nio classes to implement buffering and swapping.
    REZipOutputStream
    An alternative to ZipOutputStream that lets you write multiple zip entries at the same time.
    REZipOutputStream.Builder
    A builder class for REZipOutputStream instances.
    SwapOutputStream
    An extension of OutputStream that allows for data written to it to be recalled.
